casebody.data:
Chris D. PATTON & Roberta Lee Patton, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
DEUTSCHE BANK NATIONAL TRUST CO., Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D15-5645 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. November 07, 2017

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

The parties' joint stipulation of dismissal filed on October 26, 2017, is treated as a notice of voluntary dismissal and is accepted. This appeal is dismissed.

Appellants' motion and amended motion to tax attorney's fees are denied as moot.
